      "rationale": "Richardson extrapolation applied to three mesh levels (4.2M, 8.7M, 17.1M cells). Grid convergence index for RHI at worst-case operating point is 3.1%, which is considered of minimal impact to the hemolysis assessment conclusion under prevailing practice. Achieved level 2 confirmed."
