      "rationale": "Relative hemolysis index (RHI) is the primary QOI, directly linked to the COU acceptance criterion (RH < 1 vs. predicate). Secondary QOIs include area-averaged wall shear stress and scalar stress exposure time distributions. Selection of QOIs is consistent with FDA guidance on computational hemolysis assessment and peer-reviewed literature."
