    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are outside MRL 2 scope and appropriately deferred. The CFD hemolysis model is judged credible for use in identifying worst-case operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Validation evidence demonstrates reasonable accuracy of RHI predictions consistent with industry standard practice, and discretization errors are of minimal impact to the assessment conclusions. The requirement and acceptance criteria, while expressed in terms of industry standard expectations, are considered satisfied based on the overall weight of evidence reviewed by the assessment team.",
